snippet.textDisplay: "I had the privilege of being a colleague of Star Shah, and we taught together at the same school for two years. During our free lectures, we would often engage in deep conversations about our struggles, challenges, and future aspirations. I would sometimes express my doubts about the feasibility of succeeding in the music industry, to which Shah would respond with unwavering determination, 'I will keep chasing my passion, no matter how impossible it may seem. This dream brings me joy, and I am willing to dedicate my life to pursuing it.' His resolve was inspiring. And then, one day, he made the bold decision to leave Okara with his entire family in pursuit of his dreams. I pray that Allah blesses Shah G with even more success and happiness."
